== The Month of Wushen ==
In years whose last digit in the Western calendar is 2 or 7 (corresponding to the heavenly stems {{ill|Ren|ja|е£ђ}} and {{ill|Ding|ja|дЄБ|1=Hinoto (дЄБ)}}), the month of July is designated as the month of Wushen. (Note that in this context, вАЬmonthвАЭ may refer to a lunar month or a seasonal period [from {{ill|Rissh≈Ђ|ja|зЂЛзІЛ}} to the day before {{ill|Hakuro|ja|зЩљйЬ≤}}].)

