== The Month of Wushen ==
In years whose last digit in the Western calendar is 2 or 7 (corresponding to the heavenly stems {{ill|Ren|ja|е£ђ|1=Mizunoe (е£ђ)|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Ding|ja|дЄБ|1=Hinoto (дЄБ)|12=draft|12=draft}}), the month of July is designated as the month of Wushen. (Note that in this context, вАЬmonthвАЭ may refer to a lunar month or a seasonal period [from {{ill|Rissh≈Ђ|ja|зЂЛзІЛ|12=draft|12=draft}} to the day before {{ill|Hakuro|ja|зЩљйЬ≤|12=draft|12=draft}}].)

== The Day of Wushen ==
=== Date Selection ===
