{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}}'''Yang Earth Monkey'''{{жЛЉйЯ≥|w√єshƒУn|qq=}}гАБ{{ж≥®йЯ≥|гД®ЋЛ гДХгД£|qq=}}гАБ{{lang-ko|лђімЛ†|qq=}}гАБ{{lang-vi|{{Unicode|MбЇ≠u Th√Ґn|qq=}}|qq=}}) is one of the components of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|еЕ≠еНБеє≤жФѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}.

It is the 45th combination in the comprehensive sexagenary cycle, preceded by {{ill|Dingwei|ja|дЄБжЬ™|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Jiyou|ja|еЈ±йЕЙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. In the {{ill|Yin-Yang Five Elements theory|ja|йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, the heavenly stem {{ill|Wu|ja|жИК|1=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} represents yang earth, and the earthly branch {{ill|Shen|ja|зФ≥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} represents yang metal; according to the principle of {{ill|phase generation|ja|зЫЄзФЯ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (earth producing metal).

