It is the 45th combination in the comprehensive sexagenary cycle, preceded by {{ill|Dingwei|ja|дЄБжЬ™|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dingwei|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Jiyou|ja|еЈ±йЕЙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jiyou|qq=}}. In the {{ill|Yin-Yang Five Elements theory|ja|йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang Five Elements theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the heavenly stem {{ill|Wu|ja|жИК|1=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wu|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (жИК)|qq=}} represents yang earth, and the earthly branch {{ill|Shen|ja|зФ≥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shen|qq=}} represents yang metal; according to the principle of {{ill|phase generation|ja|зЫЄзФЯ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/phase generation|qq=}} (earth producing metal).

