{{infobox Chinese|l=Yang Earth Monkey|kanji=жИКзФ≥|romaji=tsuchinoe saru|onyomi=bojin|p=w√єshƒУn|w=wu-shen|mi=uвБµвБµ  В…Щn|y=mou6 san1|j=mou6 san1|ci=m…Рu  В…Рn|mc=m…Щu  Вin|oc-bs=m…Щ  Вin|qq=}}
{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}}'''Yang Earth Monkey'''{{жЛЉйЯ≥|w√єshƒУn|qq=}}гАБ{{ж≥®йЯ≥|гД®ЋЛ гДХгД£|qq=}}гАБ{{lang-ko|лђімЛ†|qq=}}гАБ{{lang-vi|{{Unicode|MбЇ≠u Th√Ґn|qq=}}|qq=}}) is one of the components of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|еЕ≠еНБеє≤жФѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.

It is the 45th combination in the comprehensive sexagenary cycle, preceded by {{ill|Dingwei|ja|1=Yin Fire Goat|2=ja|дЄБжЬ™|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dingwei|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Jiyou|ja|1=Yin Earth Rooster|2=ja|еЈ±йЕЙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jiyou|qq=}}. In the {{ill|Yin-Yang Five Elements theory|ja|йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang Five Elements theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the heavenly stem {{ill|Wu|ja|жИК|1=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|lt=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|2=ja|3=жИК|4=zh|5=жИК|1=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wu|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (жИК)|qq=}} represents yang earth, and the earthly branch {{ill|Shen|ja|зФ≥|1=Monkey (Zodiac)|lt=Monkey (зФ≥)|2=ja|3=зФ≥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shen|qq=}} represents yang metal; according to the principle of {{ill|phase generation|ja|зЫЄзФЯ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/phase generation|qq=}} (earth producing metal).

